Level 3 Allies to 5

From the menu, tap Quests.
Select a quest, and then select Begin.
Clearing the quest will earn experience points (EXP) for the characters who participated in the quest.
Accumulating a certain amount of EXP will raise your characters' levels.
You can earn a lot of EXP by undertaking cycle quests, available after clearing Chapter 1: Primus Island.

Kactuars will occasionally appear in cycle quests, and defeating them will earn you even more EXP.
You can also use EXP items to raise a character's level.
From the menu, tap Enhancements.
Then tap Level Up on the Enhancements screen to open an interface for leveling up.
Tap the character whose level you'd like to raise.
Using EXP items will grant the character EXP, and with enough EXP items, it is possible to level up this way, too.

Level up items can be obtained as rewards for completing daily missions.
